Package iebaker.neon.world

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Cell
    Cell is a class representing a single cell of the game world.
    CellWorld
    CellWorld is a basic class representing a 2D world made up of single Cells.
    Decoration
    Decoration is a class which represents a Decoration object which can be added to a Vertex or Edge.
    Edge
    Edge is a class which represents an edge of the Graph object.
    Entity
    Entity is a class representing an entity which is capable of occupying a grid square in CellWorld.
    Graph
    Graph is a class which represents a general mathematical graph which is composed of vertices and edges.
    Heuristic
    Class heuristic represents a way to score the estimated difficulty of reaching one Vertex from another.
    Metric
    Class Metric represents a way of scoring an Edge object based on its decorations It contains only one method, measure() which will take in an Edge and return a float representing that edge's weight.
    PerlinSampler
    PerlinSampler is a class which can create a dense grid of a certain (but expandable) intiial width and initial height, with a set vector density, and set dimensionality.
    Vertex
    Vertex is a class which represents a single Vertex in the Graph.
    Viewport
    Viewport is a class which represents a view into a CellWorld which is pannable and zoomable.
